# {{ project_name | pascal }} - Azure Service Bus Producer

Auto-generated Go producer for Azure Service Bus using `github.com/Azure/azure-sdk-for-go/sdk/messaging/azservicebus`.

## Quick start

```go
producer, err := {{ project_name | snake }}.New{{ groupname }}Producer(connectionString, "queue-or-topic")
if err != nil {
    log.Fatal(err)
}
defer producer.Close(context.Background())
```

CloudEvents are sent in structured mode by default. Use `SetContentMode({{ project_name | snake }}.ContentModeBinary)` to send data in the message body with CloudEvents attributes in `ApplicationProperties` using the `cloudEvents:` prefix.
